{"tid":1327980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過可以點樣改革警隊","createTime":"2019-07-17T19:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:51:21.000Z","uid":197424,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c63f60e5f39b35f71dffcb159d5ebf2362b5a9","tid":1327980,"uid":197424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:07:51.000Z","msg":"暫時諗到都係從薪金方面入手同採取連坐方式比少少同儕壓力佢（你地咁好兄弟應該唔會反面嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n五年內一個人被投訴 成個小隊扣薪 第一次扣10% 再犯就20/40/50% 咁罰落去 兼每月要交一份1000字工作報告比大眾 唔計標點符號（純粹想睇下班毅進仔寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n再加埋個&rdquo;工作表現改進課程&rdquo;喺你放更時候上 take attendance 要夠8成出席率+pass個final test 唔係嘅話就無薪停職等你搞掂為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cf0d20b7daa3bd66129ade13f93d0cbd7ffdfb","tid":1327980,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:15:12.000Z","msg":"慢慢j"},{"pid":"9f927c7b44ae16d3fcac3786b2c6826f3cde129a","tid":1327980,"uid":228437,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:16:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解散、完</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"16e1a4a1f1ee5373286b6732cf4597e478db7fad","tid":1327980,"uid":281584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"無民主選舉無公正法治警隊有咩制度都係死<br />\n其實一直以来都有獨立調查、持平監警會,icac,97前皇家警察有冇好似今日特衰政府犬舍咁仆街<br />\n當權者個有心利用警隊咩制度都可以改,所以係要有民主制衡當權者"},{"pid":"e145890ffb7416e9f8b86b5a2afc941deddf876e","tid":1327980,"uid":197424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01cf0d20b7daa3bd66129ade13f93d0cbd7ffdfb","tid":1327980,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:15:12.000Z","msg":"慢慢j"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:21:55.000Z","msg":"所以我開喺創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7c391355efb42fa943662e252a45c3ae8ba17f",